data.title: Victoria Azarenka
data.meta_description:
Victoria Azarenka is a Belaroushie tennis player an umwhile Warld No. 1.
She haes wan twa Australian Open singles titles, becomin the first Belaroushie player tae win a Grand Slam in singles. Her ither achievements include winnin the Bronze medal at the 2012 Simmer Olympics in Lunnon, twa mixed doubles Grand Slam teetles—the 2007 US Open wi Max Mirnyi, the 2008 French Open wi Bob Bryan—an the gowd medal in the mixed doubles at the 2012 Lunnon Olympics wi Max Mirnyi.
data.text:
Victoria Azarenka (Belaroushie: Вікторыя Фёдараўна Азаранка, Roushie: Виктория Фёдоровна Азаренко; born 31 Julie 1989) is a Belaroushie tennis player an umwhile Warld No. 1.[2] She haes wan twa Australian Open singles titles (2012 an 2013), becomin the first Belaroushie player tae win a Grand Slam in singles. Her ither achievements include winnin the Bronze medal at the 2012 Simmer Olympics in Lunnon, twa mixed doubles Grand Slam teetles—the 2007 US Open wi Max Mirnyi, the 2008 French Open wi Bob Bryan—an the gowd medal in the mixed doubles at the 2012 Lunnon Olympics wi Max Mirnyi.[3][4][5]
